It is very important to ensure that technology isn't used to limit us, but rather to take us further on a journey of opportunity and freedom.
#SoftwareFreedomDay

Today we hosted a job fair on our campus. It was an excellent opportunity for 80 graduates to meet with 19 employers face-to-face and match recruiters with the needed talents.
Thank you to ICT Association of Jordan - int@j for continuously providing remarkable support to the ICT sector, and to all the representatives from recruiting companies who came today; we wish you and your teams continued growth and success.
